        "subject": "LU-65 ORNL Lustre 2.X testing",
        "message": "LU-65 ORNL Lustre 2.X testing\n\nb=18750 Make failure handling and injection common to all\n\nThis patch moves the failure injection system lustre uses\nfor debugging into the libcfs layer so other sub systems\nof lustre can take advantage of them. For example a LNET\ndriver could set the fail_loc to test the behavior of the\nLNET layer for the case of a particular hardware failure.\n\nChange-Id: Ib7b9cf80a768bd41e72f5bb046f089351fb69073\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
